  "commonIssues": "<div class=\"accordion\" id=\"issueAccordion\"> <div class=\"card mb-2\"><div class=\"card-header\" id=\"heading1\"><h5 class=\"mb-0\"><button class=\"btn btn-link text-left\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#collapse1\" style=\"white-space: normal; word-break: break-word;\"><i class=\"fas fa-chevron-right mr-2\"></i>Sub-Registrar Office Delays</button></h5></div> <div id=\"collapse1\" class=\"collapse\"><div class=\"card-body\"><p>Delays in getting appointments and long wait times.</p><p><strong>How to fix:</strong></p><ul><li>Draft the deed and book an appointment online via the <a href=\"https://igrsup.gov.in/\" target=\"_blank\">IGRSUP Portal</a> to minimize office visits.</li></ul></div></div></div> <div class=\"card mb-2\"><div class=\"card-header\" id=\"heading2\"><h5 class=\"mb-0\"><button class=\"btn btn-link text-left collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#collapse2\" style=\"white-space: normal; word-break: break-word;\"><i class=\"fas fa-chevron-right mr-2\"></i>Drafting & Documentation Errors</button></h5></div> <div id=\"collapse2\" class=\"collapse\"><div class=\"card-body\"><p>Inaccurate property details or incomplete identification.</p><p><strong>How to fix:</strong></p><ul><li>List all assets (movable and immovable) explicitly. Bring Aadhaar cards and photographs of everyone involved.</li></ul></div></div></div> <div class=\"card mb-2\"><div class=\"card-header\" id=\"heading3\"><h5 class=\"mb-0\"><button class=\"btn btn-link text-left collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#collapse3\" style=\"white-space: normal; word-break: break-word;\"><i class=\"fas fa-chevron-right mr-2\"></i>Lack of Medical Certification</button></h5></div> <div id=\"collapse3\" class=\"collapse\"><div class=\"card-body\"><p>Allegations of the testator being of \"unsound mind\" are common in UP courts.</p><p><strong>How to fix:</strong></p><ul><li>Mandatorily attach a certificate from an MBBS/MD doctor affirming the testator's mental fitness on the day of signing.</li></ul></div></div></div> <div class=\"card mb-2\"><div class=\"card-header\" id=\"heading4\"><h5 class=\"mb-0\"><button class=\"btn btn-link text-left collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#collapse4\" style=\"white-space: normal; word-break: break-word;\"><i class=\"fas fa-chevron-right mr-2\"></i>Witness Turnaround in Court</button></h5></div> <div id=\"collapse4\" class=\"collapse\"><div class=\"card-body\"><p>Witnesses later claiming the Will wasn't made in their presence.</p><p><strong>How to fix:</strong></p><ul><li>Choose highly trusted, younger witnesses. If permitted, video record the entire execution process.</li></ul></div></div></div> <div class=\"card mb-2\"><div class=\"card-header\" id=\"heading5\"><h5 class=\"mb-0\"><button class=\"btn btn-link text-left collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#collapse5\" style=\"white-space: normal; word-break: break-word;\"><i class=\"fas fa-chevron-right mr-2\"></i>Executor & Subsequent Wills</button></h5></div> <div id=\"collapse5\" class=\"collapse\"><div class=\"card-body\"><p>Failing to appoint an executor or disputes over newer Wills.</p><p><strong>How to fix:</strong></p><ul><li>Appoint a capable, willing executor. Ensure any new Will is also registered to firmly invalidate old ones.</li></ul></div></div></div></div>"
}
